</style></head><body><div class="bespoke-marp-osc"><button data-bespoke-marp-osc="prev" tabindex="-1" title="Previous slide">Previous slide</button><span data-bespoke-marp-osc="page"></span><button data-bespoke-marp-osc="next" tabindex="-1" title="Next slide">Next slide</button><button data-bespoke-marp-osc="fullscreen" tabindex="-1" title="Toggle fullscreen (f)">Toggle fullscreen</button><button data-bespoke-marp-osc="overview" tabindex="-1" title="Toggle overview view (o)">Toggle overview view</button><button data-bespoke-marp-osc="presenter" tabindex="-1" title="Open presenter view (p)">Open presenter view</button></div><div id=":$p"><svg data-marpit-svg="" viewBox="0 0 1280 720"><foreignObject width="1280" height="720"><section id="1" data-paginate="true" data-class="title" data-theme="default" data-style="@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;700&amp;display=swap');
section {
  font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', 'Microsoft JhengHei', 'PingFang TC', 'Arial', sans-serif;
  font-size: 22px;
  padding: 40px 60px;
}
section.title {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 50%, #0f3460 100%);
  color: white;
  text-align: center;
  justify-content: center;
}
section.title h1 { color: #f0f0f0; font-size: 2em; }
section.title h2 { color: #a8d8ea; border: none; font-size: 1.2em; }
section.title p  { color: #ccc; font-size: 0.9em; }
section.act {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c3e50, #34495e);
  color: white;
  text-align: center;
  justify-content: center;
}
section.act h1 { color: #f39c12; font-size: 1.8em; }
section.act h2 { color: #ecf0f1; border: none; font-size: 1.1em; }
section.act ul  { text-align: left; color: #bdc3c7; }
h1 { color: #2c3e50; font-size: 1.4em; }
h2 { color: #27ae60; border-bottom: 2px solid #27ae60; padding-bottom: 4px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
h3 { color: #2980b9; font-size: 1em; margin-bottom: 8px; }
pre  { background: #1e1e1e; color: #d4d4d4; font-size: 0.78em; border-radius: 6px; }
code { background: #eef; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 0.9em; }
pre code { background: transparent; padding: 0; }
table { font-size: 0.85em; width: 100%; }
th { background: #2c3e50; color: white; }
td, th { padding: 6px 10px; }
tr:nth-child(even) { background: #f2f2f2; }
.red   { color: #e74c3c; font-weight: bold; }
.green { color: #27ae60; font-weight: bold; }
.blue  { color: #2980b9; font-weight: bold; }
footer { font-size: 0.7em; color: #999; }
" lang="zh-TW" class="title" data-marpit-pagination="1" style="--paginate:true;--class:title;--theme:default;--style:@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;700&amp;display=swap')
;" data-marpit-pagination-total="39" data-size="16:9">
<h1 id="%E6%A9%9F%E5%99%A8%E4%BA%BA%E5%BC%B7%E5%8C%96%E5%AD%B8%E7%BF%92%E5%AF%A6%E4%BD%9C%E8%AA%B2">機器人強化學習實作課</h1>
<h2 id="%E5%BE%9E%E6%A8%A1%E4%BB%BF%E5%AD%B8%E7%BF%92%E5%88%B0%E9%80%A3%E7%BA%8C%E5%8B%95%E4%BD%9C%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6">從模仿學習到連續動作控制</h2>
<p><strong>7 種演算法</strong></p>
<p>BC → Q-Learning → DQN → DDPG → TD3 → SAC → PPO</p>
</section>
</foreignObject></svg><svg data-marpit-svg="" viewBox="0 0 1280 720"><foreignObject width="1280" height="720"><section id="2" data-paginate="true" data-theme="default" data-style="@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;700&amp;display=swap');
