<h1 id="%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95-1behavioral-cloning">方法 1｜Behavioral Cloning</h1>
<h2 id="%E6%9C%80%E7%9B%B4%E8%A7%80%E7%9A%84%E6%83%B3%E6%B3%95%E8%AE%93%E6%A9%9F%E5%99%A8%E4%BA%BA%E7%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E6%80%8E%E9%BA%BC%E5%81%9A%E7%85%A7%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8">最直觀的想法：讓機器人看人怎麼做，照著學</h2>
<ul>
<li>收集人類（或現有 policy）的示範軌跡</li>
<li>直接做<strong>監督學習</strong>：讓 policy 模仿專家動作</li>
</ul>
<pre is="marp-pre" data-auto-scaling="downscale-only"><code class="language-python"><span class="hljs-comment"># 訓練</span>
loss = MSE(policy(state), expert_action)

<span class="hljs-comment"># 推論</span>
action = policy(state)
</code></pre>
<p><strong>優點</strong>：簡單、不需要設計獎勵函式、不需要探索</p>
<p><strong>問題是什麼？</strong></p>
</section>
