code { background: #eef; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 0.9em; }
pre code { background: transparent; padding: 0; }
table { font-size: 0.85em; width: 100%; }
th { background: #2c3e50; color: white; }
td, th { padding: 6px 10px; }
tr:nth-child(even) { background: #f2f2f2; }
.red   { color: #e74c3c; font-weight: bold; }
.green { color: #27ae60; font-weight: bold; }
.blue  { color: #2980b9; font-weight: bold; }
footer { font-size: 0.7em; color: #999; }
" lang="zh-TW" data-marpit-pagination="8" style="--paginate:true;--theme:default;--style:@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;700&amp;display=swap')
;" data-marpit-pagination-total="39" data-size="16:9">
<h1 id="%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95-2q-learning">方法 2｜Q-Learning</h1>
<h2 id="rl-%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E7%A4%8E%E8%AA%9E%E8%A8%80%E7%B5%A6%E6%A9%9F%E5%99%A8%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E7%8D%8E%E6%87%B2%E8%A8%8A%E8%99%9F%E8%AE%93%E5%AE%83%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E5%AD%B8">RL 的基礎語言：給機器人一個獎懲訊號，讓它自己學</h2>
<p><strong>三個核心概念</strong></p>
<p><strong>① Q(s, a)</strong>：在狀態 s 採取動作 a 的<strong>長期期望回報</strong></p>
<p><strong>② Bellman Equation</strong>（TD 更新）：</p>
<pre is="marp-pre" data-auto-scaling="downscale-only"><code>Q(s, a) ← Q(s, a) + α [r + γ · max Q(s', a') − Q(s, a)]
                        └─── TD 目標 ───┘  └── TD 誤差 ──┘
</code></pre>
<p><strong>③ ε-greedy 探索</strong>：</p>
<ul>
<li>以 ε 機率隨機探索（避免陷入區域性最優）</li>
<li>以 1−ε 機率選最大 Q 值的動作（利用已有知識）</li>
</ul>
</section>
</foreignObject></svg><svg data-marpit-svg="" viewBox="0 0 1280 720"><foreignObject width="1280" height="720"><section id="9" data-paginate="true" data-theme="default" data-style="@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;700&amp;display=swap');
