<h1 id="%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95-3dqndeep-q-network">方法 3｜DQN（Deep Q-Network）</h1>
<h2 id="%E7%94%A8%E7%A5%9E%E7%B6%93%E7%B6%B2%E8%B7%AF%E5%8F%96%E4%BB%A3-q-table%E8%A7%A3%E6%B1%BA%E7%84%A1%E9%99%90%E7%8B%80%E6%85%8B%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C">用神經網路取代 Q-table，解決無限狀態問題</h2>
<p><strong>DQN 的兩個關鍵設計</strong></p>
<p><strong>① Experience Replay（經驗回放）</strong></p>
<pre is="marp-pre" data-auto-scaling="downscale-only"><code class="language-python"><span class="hljs-comment"># 不直接學當前轉移，而是從 Buffer 隨機取樣</span>
batch = replay_buffer.sample(batch_size)
<span class="hljs-comment"># → 打破時序相關性，穩定訓練</span>
</code></pre>
<p><strong>② Target Network（目標網路）</strong></p>
<pre is="marp-pre" data-auto-scaling="downscale-only"><code class="language-python"><span class="hljs-comment"># TD 目標由慢更新的 target_net 決定</span>
y = r + γ · target_net(s<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;).max()
# → 固定學習目標，防止「追著自己跑」
</span></code></pre>
</section>
</foreignObject></svg><svg data-marpit-svg="" viewBox="0 0 1280 720"><foreignObject width="1280" height="720"><section id="12" data-paginate="true" data-theme="default" data-style="@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;700&amp;display=swap');
