" lang="zh-TW" data-marpit-pagination="15" style="--paginate:true;--theme:default;--style:@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;700&amp;display=swap')
;" data-marpit-pagination-total="39" data-size="16:9">
<h1 id="%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95-4ddpgdeep-deterministic-policy-gradient">方法 4｜DDPG（Deep Deterministic Policy Gradient）</h1>
<h2 id="%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E9%80%A3%E7%BA%8C%E7%9A%84%E9%A6%AC%E9%81%94%E6%89%AD%E7%9F%A9">如何控制連續的馬達扭矩？</h2>
<p><strong>Actor-Critic 架構</strong></p>
<pre is="marp-pre" data-auto-scaling="downscale-only"><code>Actor  網路：state → action（連續值，扭矩 ∈ [-2, 2]）
Critic 網路：(state, action) → Q 值（這個動作好不好？）
</code></pre>
<p><strong>與機器手臂的對應</strong>：</p>
<ul>
<li>Actor = 關節角度控制器（「現在這個姿態，施加多少扭矩？」）</li>
<li>Critic = 評估這個姿態的長期價值</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>核心程式碼</strong>：</p>
<pre is="marp-pre" data-auto-scaling="downscale-only"><code class="language-python">action = actor(state)                              <span class="hljs-comment"># 連續動作</span>
actor_loss = -critic(state, actor(state)).mean()   <span class="hljs-comment"># 讓 Q 值更高</span>
</code></pre>
</section>
</foreignObject></svg><svg data-marpit-svg="" viewBox="0 0 1280 720"><foreignObject width="1280" height="720"><section id="16" data-paginate="true" data-theme="default" data-style="@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;700&amp;display=swap');
