;--marpit-advanced-background-split:55%;" data-marpit-pagination-total="39" data-size="16:9" data-marpit-advanced-background="content" data-marpit-advanced-background-split="right">
<h2 id="ddpg-%E8%A8%93%E7%B7%B4%E7%B5%90%E6%9E%9C">DDPG 訓練結果</h2>

<p><strong>環境</strong>：Pendulum-v1（單關節扭矩控制）</p>
<p><strong>結果</strong>：</p>
<ul>
<li>最佳 eval = <strong>-101.6</strong>（接近最優 -100）<img class="emoji" draggable="false" alt="🎉" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/jdecked/twemoji@17.0.2/assets/svg/1f389.svg" data-marp-twemoji=""/></li>
<li>但訓練曲線震盪劇烈</li>
<li>高標準差：策略不穩定</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>DDPG 的三個已知問題</strong>：</p>
<ol>
<li>Q 值<strong>高估</strong>（max 運算元偏差）</li>
<li>Actor <strong>更新太快</strong>，Critic 還沒學好</li>
<li>過擬合特定動作，<strong>探索不足</strong></li>
</ol>
</section>
