" lang="zh-TW" data-marpit-pagination="18" style="--paginate:true;--theme:default;--style:@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;700&amp;display=swap')
;" data-marpit-pagination-total="39" data-size="16:9">
<h1 id="%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95-5td3twin-delayed-deep-deterministic">方法 5｜TD3（Twin Delayed Deep Deterministic）</h1>
<h2 id="ddpg-%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%89%E5%80%8B%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8Ctd3-%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E4%BF%AE%E6%8E%89">DDPG 的三個問題，TD3 一次修掉</h2>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>問題</th>
<th>TD3 的解法</th>
<th>程式碼改動</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>Q 值高估</td>
<td><strong>Twin Critics</strong>：取兩個 Critic 的最小值</td>
<td>+1 個 Critic 網路</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Actor 更新太快</td>
<td><strong>Delayed Actor Update</strong>：每 2 步才更新 Actor</td>
<td><code>if step % 2 == 0</code></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>探索不足</td>
<td><strong>Target Policy Smoothing</strong>：目標動作加入雜訊</td>
<td><code>a' += clip(noise, -c, c)</code></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p><strong>完整 TD 目標</strong>：</p>
<pre is="marp-pre" data-auto-scaling="downscale-only"><code class="language-python">a_next  = target_actor(s<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;) + clip(noise, -c, c)   # 平滑雜訊
q1, q2  = target_critic1(s&#x27;</span>, a_next), target_critic2(s<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;, a_next)
y       = r + γ · min(q1, q2)                      # Twin Critic 取最小
</span></code></pre>
</section>
