;" data-marpit-pagination-total="39" data-size="16:9">
<h2 id="%E4%B8%89%E7%A8%AE%E9%80%A3%E7%BA%8C%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E6%BC%94%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E5%B0%8D%E6%AF%94">三種連續控制演算法對比</h2>
<p><strong>Pendulum-v1</strong>（回報越靠近 0 越好）：</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>演算法</th>
<th>最佳 Eval</th>
<th>步數</th>
<th>訓練穩定性</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><strong>DDPG</strong></td>
<td><strong>-101.6</strong></td>
<td>100K</td>
<td>低（高方差）</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>TD3</td>
<td>-119.8</td>
<td>70K</td>
<td>中（更穩）</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>SAC</td>
<td>-171.8</td>
<td>100K</td>
<td>高（但過度探索）</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p><strong>LunarLanderContinuous-v3</strong>：</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>演算法</th>
<th>eval ≥ 200 達成步數</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>PPO</td>
<td>~163K 步</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>SAC</strong></td>
<td><strong>~50K 步</strong> ← 樣本效率碾壓</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>SAC 的競爭力不在極簡任務，而在多軸連續控制</strong></p>
</blockquote>
</section>
