;--marpit-advanced-background-split:45%;" data-marpit-pagination-total="39" data-size="16:9" data-marpit-advanced-background="content" data-marpit-advanced-background-split="right">
<h1 id="%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95-7ppoproximal-policy-optimization">方法 7｜PPO（Proximal Policy Optimization）</h1>
<h2 id="%E5%85%88%E7%9C%8B-reinforce-%E7%9A%84%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C">先看 REINFORCE 的問題</h2>
<p><strong>REINFORCE</strong>（最基本的 Policy Gradient）：</p>
<pre is="marp-pre" data-auto-scaling="downscale-only"><code class="language-python">loss = -log π(a|s) × G_t   <span class="hljs-comment"># 直接對回報加權做梯度上升</span>
</code></pre>
<p><strong>問題</strong>：每次更新幅度<strong>無限制</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>一次更新走太遠 → 策略崩潰</li>
<li>崩潰後很難恢復</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>實際結果</strong>（我們跑的）：</p>
</section>
