" lang="zh-TW" data-marpit-pagination="28" style="--paginate:true;--theme:default;--style:@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;700&amp;display=swap')
;" data-marpit-pagination-total="39" data-size="16:9">
<h2 id="ppo-%E7%9A%84%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0clipped-objective">PPO 的核心創新：Clipped Objective</h2>
<p><strong>PPO 的限制更新幅度</strong>：</p>
<pre is="marp-pre" data-auto-scaling="downscale-only"><code class="language-python">ratio = π_new(a|s) / π_old(a|s)   <span class="hljs-comment"># 新舊策略的比值</span>

loss = -<span class="hljs-built_in">min</span>(
    ratio * A,                      <span class="hljs-comment"># 原始目標</span>
    clip(ratio, <span class="hljs-number">1</span>-ε, <span class="hljs-number">1</span>+ε) * A      <span class="hljs-comment"># 裁剪版本</span>
)
<span class="hljs-comment"># 「每次更新不能走太遠，</span>
<span class="hljs-comment">#   新策略和舊策略的差距要在安全範圍內。」</span>
</code></pre>
<p><strong>優點</strong>：</p>
<ul>
<li>單次更新有上界 → 策略不會崩潰</li>
<li>可以在同一批資料上多次更新（<code>n_epochs</code>）</li>
<li>實作簡單，穩定性極高</li>
</ul>
</section>
</foreignObject></svg><svg data-marpit-svg="" viewBox="0 0 1280 720"><foreignObject width="1280" height="720"><section id="29" data-paginate="true" data-theme="default" data-style="@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;700&amp;display=swap');
