<h2 id="reinforce-vs-ppo">REINFORCE vs PPO</h2>

<p><strong>CartPole-v1</strong>：</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>演算法</th>
<th>最終 Eval</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>REINFORCE</td>
<td><strong>9.5</strong>（卡住）</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>PPO</strong></td>
<td><strong>500</strong>（滿分）</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p><strong>LunarLander-v3</strong>：</p>
<ul>
<li>PPO eval ≈ <strong>284</strong></li>
<li>穩定收斂，訓練曲線平滑</li>
</ul>
