" lang="zh-TW" data-marpit-pagination="38" style="--paginate:true;--theme:default;--style:@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;700&amp;display=swap')
;" data-marpit-pagination-total="39" data-size="16:9">
<h2 id="%E9%99%84%E9%8C%84-b%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E5%B9%95%E8%B6%85%E5%8F%83%E6%95%B8%E9%80%9F%E6%9F%A5">附錄 B｜第二幕超參數速查</h2>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>演算法</th>
<th>檔案</th>
<th>關鍵行</th>
<th>最重要超參數</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><strong>DDPG</strong></td>
<td><code>04_Actor_Critic_Continuous/2015_DDPG/train.py</code></td>
<td>82–85</td>
<td><code>lr_actor=1e-4</code> <code>lr_critic=1e-3</code> <code>tau=0.005</code></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>TD3</strong></td>
<td><code>04_Actor_Critic_Continuous/2018_TD3/train.py</code></td>
<td>75–77</td>
<td><code>lr=3e-4</code> <code>buffer=200K</code> <code>batch=256</code></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>SAC</strong></td>
<td><code>04_Actor_Critic_Continuous/2018_SAC/train.py</code></td>
<td>73–75</td>
<td><code>lr=3e-4</code> <code>tau=0.005</code> <code>alpha=自動</code></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p><strong>Pendulum-v1 結果</strong>（eval 越接近 0 越好，最優 ≈ −100）：</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th></th>
<th>DDPG</th>
<th>TD3</th>
<th>SAC</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>最佳 Eval</td>
<td><strong>−101.6</strong></td>
<td>−119.8</td>
<td>−171.8</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>收斂步數</td>
<td>100K</td>
<td><strong>70K</strong></td>
<td>100K</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>方差</td>
<td>高 <img class="emoji" draggable="false" alt="❌" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/jdecked/twemoji@17.0.2/assets/svg/274c.svg" data-marp-twemoji=""/></td>
<td>中 <img class="emoji" draggable="false" alt="✅" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/jdecked/twemoji@17.0.2/assets/svg/2705.svg" data-marp-twemoji=""/></td>
<td>低（過探索）</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</section>
</foreignObject></svg><svg data-marpit-svg="" viewBox="0 0 1280 720"><foreignObject width="1280" height="720"><section id="39" data-paginate="true" data-theme="default" data-style="@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;700&amp;display=swap');
section {
  font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', 'Microsoft JhengHei', 'PingFang TC', 'Arial', sans-serif;
  font-size: 22px;
  padding: 40px 60px;
}
section.title {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 50%, #0f3460 100%);
  color: white;
  text-align: center;
  justify-content: center;
}
section.title h1 { color: #f0f0f0; font-size: 2em; }
section.title h2 { color: #a8d8ea; border: none; font-size: 1.2em; }
section.title p  { color: #ccc; font-size: 0.9em; }
section.act {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c3e50, #34495e);
  color: white;
  text-align: center;
  justify-content: center;
}
section.act h1 { color: #f39c12; font-size: 1.8em; }
section.act h2 { color: #ecf0f1; border: none; font-size: 1.1em; }
section.act ul  { text-align: left; color: #bdc3c7; }
h1 { color: #2c3e50; font-size: 1.4em; }
h2 { color: #27ae60; border-bottom: 2px solid #27ae60; padding-bottom: 4px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
h3 { color: #2980b9; font-size: 1em; margin-bottom: 8px; }
pre  { background: #1e1e1e; color: #d4d4d4; font-size: 0.78em; border-radius: 6px; }
code { background: #eef; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 0.9em; }
pre code { background: transparent; padding: 0; }
table { font-size: 0.85em; width: 100%; }
th { background: #2c3e50; color: white; }
td, th { padding: 6px 10px; }
tr:nth-child(even) { background: #f2f2f2; }
.red   { color: #e74c3c; font-weight: bold; }
.green { color: #27ae60; font-weight: bold; }
.blue  { color: #2980b9; font-weight: bold; }
footer { font-size: 0.7em; color: #999; }
" lang="zh-TW" data-marpit-pagination="39" style="--paginate:true;--theme:default;--style:@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;700&amp;display=swap')
;" data-marpit-pagination-total="39" data-size="16:9">
<h2 id="%E9%99%84%E9%8C%84-c%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E5%B9%95%E8%B6%85%E5%8F%83%E6%95%B8%E9%80%9F%E6%9F%A5">附錄 C｜第三幕超參數速查</h2>
<p><strong>PPO</strong> — <code>03_Policy_Gradient/2017_PPO/train.py</code>，行 96–101</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>超參數</th>
<th>值</th>
<th>作用</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><code>lr</code></td>
<td>3e-4</td>
<td>學習率</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code>n_steps</code></td>
<td>2048</td>
<td>每次收集多少步再更新</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code>clip_range</code> ε</td>
<td><strong>0.2</strong></td>
<td>每次更新最多改變 ±20%（核心！）</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code>n_epochs</code></td>
<td>≈ 10</td>
<td>同一批資料重複訓練幾次</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p><strong>結果對比</strong>：</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>演算法</th>
<th>CartPole</th>
<th>步數</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>REINFORCE</td>
<td>9.5（失敗）</td>
<td>50K episodes</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>DQN</td>
<td>500（滿分）</td>
<td>150K</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>PPO</strong></td>
<td><strong>500（滿分）</strong></td>
<td><strong>20K</strong> ← 最快</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</section>
